# Files wrangler must NOT upload as static assets.
# THE FIX (2026-07-08): a fresh clone packs the whole ~44MB history into one
# pack file that exceeds Cloudflare's 25 MiB per-asset limit — wrangler was
# trying to upload .git/objects/pack/*.pack and every deploy failed ("Asset too
# large"). None of these dirs are served by the game.
.git/
node_modules/
scripts/
server/
keystone_inbox/
